    "text": "With <@U01DWJSAF2B> we have been working for some months on a digital-first book \"for JavaScript programmers who want to learn the nuts and bolts of WebAssembly. You'll go from hand crafting bytecodes to building a real compiler for a simple programming language.\"\n\n:bird: <https://twitter.com/dubroy/status/1622987684946796544|Announcement Tweet>\n\nOn top of writing a book we are exploring what's possible if we create content ignoring the constraints of \"printing dead words\".\n\nFollow <https://twitter.com/WasmGroundUp|WasmGroundUp> for updates, or sign up at <https://wasmfromthegroundup.com>.",
